Package: mixvarselect
Type: Package
Title: Mixture of expert modelling with variable selection using penalization
Version: 1.0
Date: 2012-03-07
Author: Vahid Partovi Nia and Abbas Khalili
Maintainer: Vahid Partovi Nia <vahid.partovinia@polymtl.ca>
Depends: R (>= 2.14.1)
Description: The package uses Ridge, Lasso and SCAD penlization to implement variable selection and regularization in various parameters of mixutres of Gaussians. The package offers variable selection for the mean compoenents and logit of mixture proportions. The package requires installation of GSL libraries on the machine and may not work under Windows platform.
License:  GPL (>= 2)

